No. I'm convinced.

1697
01:29:02,754 --> 01:29:04,422
Not guilty.

1698
01:29:04,423 --> 01:29:06,298
What's the matter with you?

1699
01:29:06,299 --> 01:29:08,300
I have a reasonable doubt now.

1700
01:29:08,301 --> 01:29:09,927
Eleven to one.

1701
01:29:09,928 --> 01:29:12,930
